'''Becky Ngoma''', ni umukinnyi [[Zambiya|wa]] filime wa [[Zambiya]] akaba n'umwanditsi<ref>https://www.imdb.com/name/nm4145631/</ref>.  Umukinnyi wa firime, Mwape yatangiye umwuga we nk'umukinnyi kandi azwi cyane kubera uruhare muri ''Mwansa the Great'', ''I Am Not A Witch'' and ''Temzu Town''.<ref>https://justfilms.co/portfolio_page/temzu-town/</ref>  Usibye gukina, ni umuyobozi na producer.<ref>https://kerrinkokot.com/portfolio/temzu-town/</ref>

== Ubuzima bwite ==
She was born in [[Lusaka]], Zambia. She is a graduate of TV production at Zambia Institute of Mass Communication (ZAMCOM)<ref>http://www.daily-mail.co.zm/from-play-circle-to-zuba/</ref>.

== Umwuga ==
''Yakoze nk'umukinnyi w'amafirime'' n'umwanditsi mu biganiro byinshi bya televiziyo 'nka, Kabanana, Ikinamico ya mbere muri [[Zambiya]] na ''Love Games na Fever'' ndetse no muri firime, ''Suwi'' na ''Mwansa the Great''<ref>https://www.filmaffinity.com/us/film708409.html</ref>''.'' .  Hagati aho, yakoraga kuri opera ikunzwe cyane yo muri [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afrika]] yepfo,''Generations'' <ref>http://africanwomenincinema.blogspot.com/2018/11/african-women-in-cinema-blog-updates.html</ref>. Ni n'umwanditsi wa seri izwi cyane ''Zuba'', telenovela ya mbere muri [[Zambiya]], yerekana kuri Zambezi Magic. Yakinnye kandi muri filime ashimwa cyane  kuri ''I Am Not a Witch'' yabaye filime yatsindiye BAFTA afite uruhare 'Bwalya'.<ref>https://magazine.uzacoona.com/qa-becky-ngoma-talks-about-her-writing-journey/</ref>  

Yatsindiye ibihembo byinshi kubuhanga bwe bwo kwandika-kwandika nka; Igihembo cya Filime, Televiziyo na Radiyo [[Zambiya]] 2014 (Zafta) igihembo cy’umwanditsi mwiza, igihembo cya Zafta cya 2016 kuri filimi nziza, na 2018 ibihembo by’abagore bo muri [[Zambiya]] ku mugore w’umwaka<ref>https://africafilmproducers.org/membership/becky-ngoma-2/</ref>. 

